Anna Faith AKA Elsa From Frozen AKA My One To Watch 2016 Has Officially Graduated Nate | Email 
I’ve blogged about this girl on and off for a year. She originally got famous for looking just like the Frozen character, and then my keen eye realized she was destined for greater things. I named her one to watch in 2016 with Bella Thorne, and boy I couldn’t have been more right about both. While Bella is a mixed drink away from flashing posting a sex tape on Snapchat, Anna Faith has been sneakily posting Instagram pictures to the point she is no longer “Elsa from Frozen girl”, is is just a straight up Instagram girl status. No longer one to watch, she’s in the AP Top 25.
